CONVERSATION B: Dynamic Threshold Expansion (conv-expand-001)
Tests that expansion mechanism activates on repeated "more" requests.
Pipeline checks: expansion flag (YES/NO), threshold calculation, expansion level.
All checks verify mechanism runs — exact values depend on LLM intent classification.
==========================================================================
––– comment –––
