==========================================================================
CONVERSATION H: Follow-up Context Questions (conv-followup-001)
Tests CONTENT_QUESTION intent — context-dependent follow-up queries that reference
previous results. These queries rely on the plugin reusing prior search context
instead of performing a new KNN search.
  H1: Initial query about TV shows → Entertainment sources (baseline)
  H2: Follow-up "Who are the main characters?" → expects valid response
  H3: Clarification "I meant the one about the drug dealer" → expects valid response
==========================================================================
