==========================================================================
CONVERSATION I: Real-world User Scenarios (conv-realworld-001)
Tests realistic user queries that reflect how people actually interact with
a conversational RAG system — mood-based requests, genre preferences,
character questions, and similarity-based recommendations.
  I1: "Im bored, suggest something to watch" → Entertainment sources
  I2: "I want something funny" → The Office (comedy) in sources
  I3: "Who is Walter White?" → Breaking Bad in sources
  I4: "Something similar but with sci-fi elements" → Stranger Things/Mandalorian
  I5: "What programming language should I learn for web development?" → Programming sources
==========================================================================
––– comment –––
